Included in the 
<taxonomicName id="49FB89E7FFEBFF8BE46BA34BB39D3248" authorityName="Scherrer &amp; Aguiar" authorityYear="2012" box="[530,660,1556,1580]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Debilos" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="25" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="typurum">
<emphasis id="BC8F2E76FFEBFF8BE46BA34BB32F3248" box="[530,550,1557,1580]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">D</emphasis>
. 
